Description: Reading, manipulating, writing and plotting
    spatiotemporal arrays (raster and vector data cubes) in 'R', using 'GDAL'
    bindings provided by 'sf', and 'NetCDF' bindings by 'ncmeta' and 'RNetCDF'.
